Enjoy!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Hope, the library will save you time and bring some joy when
writing scripts interacting with the Nitrate server. Looking
forward to your feedback, comments, suggestions and patches ;-)


